description:
A carefully considered design, sleek contemporary interiors and a peaceful sizeable yard unite in this stylish duplex to deliver an idyllic family home of space and flexibility.

Brimming with natural light, this home features a clever layout offering open plan living/dining areas with crisp coastal decor, while sliding doors retract to allow a seamless transition to a superb entertainers' yard at the rear.

A gourmet kitchen is equipped with only the highest of quality appliances and abundant cupboard storage including a large pantry.

The three bedrooms are all well-proportioned and appointed with wardrobes and ceiling fans, while the master features an ensuite. Additional features include a bright and airy fully tiled main bathroom and a substantial Double lock up garage.

Boasting an effortless transition from inside living to your very own private sun-soaked flat yard there is ample room for the kids and your fury friends.

With the Baringa State High School, Shopping Centre and and medical facilities now open, this is a great place to live or invest.

This property is ideally located, with only a one hour drive to Brisbane, 30 minute drive to the Sunshine Coast Airport, 12 minute drive to the Sunshine Coast University Hospital, and several pristine beaches nearby.

Features we love:

3 bed | 2 bath | 2 car
Generously scaled layout features open plan living/dining
Effortless flow to outdoor area
Streamlined kitchen w/ quality appliances
Generous bedrooms with robes
Master with modern ensuite
Double car garage
Minutes to Baringa shops, schools and the tavern
